  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate the effectiveness of an additive complex āyurvedic
      diagnosis and treatment compared to conventional standard care alone in stationary patients
      with Fibromyalgia Syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
